re":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"到了歐洲尋求<br />\n政治庇護的手足<br />\n可能最後會被遣返"},{"pid":"3a67a1ce652bcb2d286142a0a71b7034917a9691","tid":2330740,"uid":48234,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請<br />\n問<br />\n邪惡熨斗<br />\n(狗隻#159448)<br />\n你<br />\n屙<br />\n尿<br />\n嗰<br />\n陣<br />\n起<br />\n左<br />\n腳<br />\n定<br />\n右<br />\n腳<br />\n?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439807</a><br />\n邪惡熨斗(狗隻#159448)，你老婆係水炮車啊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775904</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"f614f3a9ed80063d54b9cd3176780671daaa4efd","tid":2330740,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"係咪總之同中共做生意=奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}